<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>LET US CROWN HIM</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu min thilbawlthei pak un,
 Angelte'n le pak hen;
 Lallukhuk chu hun lau in la,
 Khuksak un mitin Lal.

[V2]
 Khuksak hitiu, Khuksak hitiu,
 Khuksak hitiu, Tanpa Lien mitin Lal chuh;
 Khuksak hitiu, Khuksak hitiu, Lal chuh,
 Khuksak hitiu, mitin Lal.

[V3]
 2. Namtin leh phung tina mite,
 Sietlei chung a umte'n;
 Lalna cheng chu Amah pie'i tiu,
 Khuksak un mitin Lal.

[V4]
 3. Chunglama zatam mel muhloh tawh,
 A keng bul akhun; ding;
 Kumsawt la chuh sak pih hih hi ting,
 Khuksak ding mitin Lal.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>31</hymn_number>
</song>